&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Natural problem-solvers, who enjoy tackling fresh challenges each day&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Team players: to succeed, SWEs must be able to build strong relationships with those around them&lt;/li&gt;
