&lt;li&gt;Basic knowledge of Linux operating systems and networking protocols&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;CCNA certification is a plus&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proven experience in racking, cabling, and working with&amp;nbsp;&lt;span data-markjs=&quot;true&quot;&gt;data&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;center facilities management tools (power, cooling, etc.)&lt;/li&gt;
