&lt;li&gt;Strong ability to manage time effectively, prioritize tasks in a fast-paced environment, and adapt to changing requirements&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A collaborative mindset, with the ability to work both independently and as part of a team, often with minimal supervision&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to safely lift and move equipment weighing up to 60 pounds&lt;/li&gt;
